column1: IF ccr_ll_oxo_etio_d is MF 0 AND ccr_a_cortolone_d is MF 1 AND ccr_etio_d is MF 0 THEN 4_Obese is MF 1 AND 2_Normal is MF 0 AND 3_Surpoid is MF 1
IF ccr_s_ad_17b_d is MF 0 AND ccr_zob_dhf_d is MF 1 THEN 1_SousPoid is MF 0
IF ccr_ths_d is MF 0 AND ccr_pd_d is MF 1 AND ccr_thf_d is MF 0 THEN 2_Normal is MF 0 AND 3_Surpoid is MF 0 AND 1_SousPoid is MF 1
IF ccr_pt_one_d is MF 2 THEN 3_Surpoid is MF 1 AND 5_ExtremeObese is MF 1
IF ccr_zoa_dhe_d is MF 2 THEN 5_ExtremeObese is MF 0
